안녕하세요 복희예요 !

저의 영상 중 신전떡볶이 먹방영상(https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WQK36RBTia4) 에서 1:47에 “혼자 아니야” 라고 말하는 듯한 여자의 말소리가 들린다는 댓글이 많이 달렸더라구요

많은 분들이 무슨 소린지 궁금해 하셔서 소리를 분석하는 전문기관에 의뢰를 했는데 조금 전에 결과가 나왔어요 !
게시글로 올리려고했는데 스펙토그램으로 분석된 주파수 그래프를 보여드리는게 좋을 것 같아서 영상으로 올립니다 !

성문분석 결과 ““혼자 아니야”라고 들리는 것으로 의심되는 청취 구간에서 성문이 관찰되지 않고, 청취 구간에 대해 음절 단위로 분석했을 때에 ‘혼’과 같은 소리로 청음되지 않는다. 따라서 의심되는 청취 구간은 사람이나 다른 목소리일 가능성이 매우 낮다“이라는 소견을 받았습니다.  

따라서 해당부분은 “음식물을 씹고 삼키는 소리와 숨소리가 겹쳐서, 소리가 증폭되는 ASMR의 특성에 의해 녹음이나 편집과정에서 발생된 소리 같다”는 의견이었습니다 🙂

translation:




Hello, this is Bokhee!


In my video, there was a lot of comments that I heard the voice of a woman who seemed to say "I'm not alone" at 1:47 in the Shinjeon Tteokbokki Meokbang video (https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WQK36RBTia4).


Many of you were wondering what I was talking about, so I turned to a professional organization that analyzes sounds, but the results came out a while ago!
I tried to post it, but I think it would be better to show the frequency graph analyzed by the spectrogram, so I upload it as a video!


As a result of analyzing the voiceprint, the voiceprint is not observed in the listening section suspected of hearing “I am not alone,” and when the listening section is analyzed in syllable units, it is not heard with a “horn” -like sound. Therefore, the suspected listening section is very unlikely to be a human or other voice. ”


Therefore, the relevant part was the opinion that “the sound of chewing and swallowing food and the sound of breath overlapped, and the sound is amplified by the characteristic of ASMR, which is the sound generated during the recording or editing process” 🙂


I hope that the curiosity of Bok Dung Hee will be solved even a little 🙏🏻 Then see you in a more delicious video 🙌🏻
